    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-03-06T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-03-06T11:00:00-05:00" n="938"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d938">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">867.00/3124: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ankara</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-03-06T18:00:00+02:00"
                            >March 6, 1942—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received March 7—1:47 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>124. Reference my 123, March 6. I have been informed in confidence by an entirely
                    reliable source that the accomplices of the man killed in the bomb explosion,
                    who have now been arrested by the Turkish police have by their confessions
                    implicated several members of the Soviet Embassy in Ankara. My informant further
                    states that one of the accomplices has taken refuge at the Soviet Consulate
                    General in Istanbul, that the Consul General has thus far refused to allow the
                    police to interrogate him and that the police have requested the Soviet
                    Ambassador’s permission to enter the premises threatening to enter by force if
                    necessary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
